title: G'zOne CA-201L
extended_title: Casio G'zOne CA-201L Android smartphone. Announced Mar 2013. Features 4.0″  display, Snapdragon S4 Plus chipset, 8 MP primary camera, 1.3 MP front camera, 1800 mAh battery, 16 GB storage, 1000 MB RAM, MIL-STD-810G compliant, Corning Gorilla Glass 2.

title: G'zOne Commando
extended_title: Casio G'zOne Commando Android smartphone. Announced Apr 2011. Features 3.6″  display, 5 MP primary camera, 1460 mAh battery, 1000 MB storage, 512 MB RAM, MIL-STD-810G compliant.

title: G'zOne Ravine 2

title: G'zOne Ravine

title: G'zOne Brigade
